# Bug Fixes: Layout & Functionality

## Goal Description
Fix the `RenderFlex` overflow crash in [SuperThanksScreen](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/super_thanks_screen.dart#7-13) and address the reported "broken" slide-to-save functionality.

## Proposed Changes

### Screens

#### [MODIFY] [super_thanks_screen.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/super_thanks_screen.dart)
- **Problem**: `Spacer()` was used inside a `SingleChildScrollView`, causing infinite height constraint error.
- **Fix**: Restructure the layout. Use a parent `Column` containing:
    1. `Expanded` -> `SingleChildScrollView` (for scrollable content).
    2. `Padding` -> [Button](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/today_screen.dart#1051-1089) (pinned to bottom).

#### [MODIFY] [today_screen.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/today_screen.dart)
- **Safeguards**: Add `mounted` check in [_autoSave](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/today_screen.dart#282-320) before any state updates to prevent "dirty widget" errors.

#### [MODIFY] [swipe_to_save_widget.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/widgets/swipe_to_save_widget.dart)
- **Gesture Handling**: Ensure `GestureDetector` logic is robust.
- **Feedback**: Verify completion logic resets correctly if action fails (though action is void callback).

